  07 Apr 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.4.0.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64 to KEYWORDS; bug #88069

*msmtp-1.4.0 (07 Apr 2005)

  07 Apr 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.3.6.ebuild,
  +msmtp-1.4.0.ebuild:
  DEPEND on GnuTLS 1.2.0 and above instead of 1.1.23 and above. Fix use_enable
  for GSASL.

  09 Mar 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.3.6.ebuild:
  Initial ~sparc.

  22 Feb 2005; Aaron Kulbe <superlag@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.3.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on PPC

  07 Feb 2005; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.3.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

*msmtp-1.3.6 (06 Feb 2005)

  06 Feb 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.3.6.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.3.6.

*msmtp-1.3.5

  06 Feb 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.3.5.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.3.5.

*msmtp-1.3.4 (22 Jan 2005)

  22 Jan 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> -msmtp-1.2.3.ebuild,
  msmtp-1.3.2-r1.ebuild, +msmtp-1.3.4.ebuild:
  Version bump, stabilise 1.3.2-r1 on amd64, purge 1.2.3.

  22 Jan 2005; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

*msmtp-1.3.2-r1 (14 Jan 2005)

  14 Jan 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.3.2-r1.ebuild:
  Added mailwrapper and virtual/mta functionality, resolving bug 77398.

  04 Jan 2005; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

  03 Jan 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64.

  03 Jan 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

*msmtp-1.3.2 (29 Dec 2004)

  29 Dec 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.3.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*msmtp-1.3.1 (25 Dec 2004)

  25 Dec 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.3.1.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  23 Dec 2004; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64 to KEYWORDS; bug #74100

  15 Dec 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.3.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

  14 Dec 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Stabilise on amd64, tidy use invocation slightly (cosmetic)

  03 Dec 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.3.ebuild,
  msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  einstall -> make DESTDIR=${D} install

  24 Nov 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> -msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild,
  -msmtp-1.2.2.ebuild, msmtp-1.2.3.ebuild:
  Marked 1.2.3 stable on amd64, purged old versions.

*msmtp-1.2.4 (11 Oct 2004)

  11 Oct 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> -msmtp-1.1.2-r1.ebuild,
  -msmtp-1.1.3.ebuild, msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild, +msmtp-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Version bump -> 1.2.4. Removed outdated 1.1.x series ebuilds. 1.2.1 stable
  on amd64.

*msmtp-1.2.3 (07 Sep 2004)

  07 Sep 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.2.3.ebuild:
  Version bump, fixes bug #62968. Reported by Martin Lambers <marlam@web.de>.
  Added dev-util/pkgconfig to DEPEND.

*msmtp-1.2.2 (01 Sep 2004)

  01 Sep 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Closes #60609, reported by Daniel Webert
  <rockoo@rockoo.homelinux.org>. Also specified minimal version number for
  dev-libs/openssl dependency to 0.9.6 (according to upstream doc) for
  msmtp-1.2.2 and -1.2.1.

  10 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Add virtual/libc DEPEND.

  10 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> -msmtp-1.0.0.ebuild,
  -msmtp-1.1.2.ebuild:
  Remove aging ebuilds.

  10 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild:
  I didn't really improve it at all, sorry Mr_Bones_.

  08 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Improve USE flag handling.

  03 Aug 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild:
  fix use invocation

*msmtp-1.2.1 (01 Aug 2004)

  01 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild:
