*msmtp-1.1.2-r1 (08 Jul 2004)

  08 Jul 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.1.2-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bumped for gsasl support, through virtual/gsasl. Temporarily removed
  ~ppc and ~x86 till someone can test this.

